io.github.prolobjectlink.prolog

Interface PrologOperator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<PrologOperator>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractOperator

    public interface PrologOperator
extends Comparable<PrologOperator>
    This class defines a Prolog operator. Prolog operators are composed by a string operator name, string operator specifier or type and a operator priority. Extends from Comparable to compare with others operators instance over priority property.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Jose Zalacain
